    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2004-09-15</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-09-22T19:18:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Close the Bank Examiner Revolving Door Act - Amends the Federal Deposit Insurance Act to prohibit certain former Federal bank examiners and other banking supervisory personnel from holding office, position, or employment at a depository institution during the one-year period following cessation of their Federal service.</p> <p>Mandates forfeiture of Federal retirement and other benefits for violations of this Act.</p> <p> Requires the head of any Federal banking agency to report such a violation to the Director of the Office of Personnel Management.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
